-- Raia Drogasil Plans to Buy Two Goias Drugstore Chains
-- B y   J o s e   S e r g i o   O s s e
-- 2012-05-24T21:52:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-24/raia-drogasil-plans-to-buy-two-goias-drugstore-chains-correct-.html
(Corrects number of targeted chains in headline, first
paragraph.)  Raia Drogasil SA said it signed a
letter of intention to buy two drugstore chains in the Brazilian
state of Goias, according to a regulatory filing.  The acquisition is pending regulatory approval, said the
company, without disclosing the financial terms of the
operation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
